                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 774/411.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">King</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Bangkok</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1908-11-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 28, 1908</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Siamese Government entirely indorse the Government of the United States’s
                    sympathy with Chinese Government in bereavement. Would not object postponement
                    Opium International Conference to 1st next February.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">King.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
